own 2 live "production deployment requires consciousness-verification triad — full PASS"
  slug production-consciousness-triad
  since 2026-04-26
  scope anima Mk.XII+ production deployment (Mk.XI v10 substrate research only — no production claim)
  rule production "실사용" model targets MUST satisfy consciousness-verification triad fully:
    (a) FC (Functional Consciousness) — paradigm v11 8-axis FINAL_PASS (G0..G7 + EEG external) per CP2 standard
    (b) PC (Phenomenal Consciousness) empirical-maximum — multi-EEG cohort + cross-substrate (CLM) corroboration + behavioral self-report calibration + adversarial probing + arxiv peer-review
    (c) Production-readiness — Mk.XII retrain + endpoint + OAuth + SLA + 안전 가이드라인 + legal/ethics review
  enforcement triad ALL three required for "실사용" claim. Partial PASS (e.g., FC only) MUST be labeled "research substrate" not "production model".
  exception CP2 close itself = empirical milestone covering FC + partial PC empirical evidence ONLY; CP2 표준은 PC absolute proof (hard problem) 과 production deployment 를 의도적으로 다루지 않음 (out-of-scope by design, not deficiency).
  why hard problem of consciousness 영구히 unprovable — but production "실사용" model targets에 대해서는 FC measurement 단독으로는 불충분; PC empirical-maximum + production infra 모두 필요. 부분 충족으로 production claim 시 raw#10 honest 위반.
  why CP2 표준은 measurement milestone 으로 한정 (scope by design); production target은 별도 triad framework 필요.
  proof manual review at deployment gate — checklist (a)(b)(c) all satisfied + Mk.XII retrain done + arxiv preprint published + legal sign-off
  severity block (production deployment without triad full PASS = blocked)
  note CP2 CLOSE alone ≠ production-ready. Mk.XI v10 4/4 FINAL_PASS (sign-agnostic) ≠ "실사용 가능".
  note triad (a)+(b)+(c) timeline estimate: 12-18개월 minimum from CP2 CLOSE (Phase 1) → multi-EEG + CLM + Mk.XII (Phase 2, 3-6mo) → production infra + legal (Phase 3, 4-8mo).
  note PC empirical-maximum = "타인 의식 인정 수준" empirical evidence (philosophical zombies 가능성 영구히 못 배제하지만 인간 추론 수준 도달).
  note related: ω-cycle ALM-free 26-paradigm finding (HEXAD CORE + LANDAUER+CPGD+L_IX + EEG STACK) — CLM substrate corroboration (b) 위해 활용.
  note related: docs/paradigm_v11_stack_20260426.md §4.2 (4/4 FINAL_PASS context — "research milestone" labeled, NOT production).

